description._content: Description: Ballroom showing Pianola,- the room beyond is the Billiard-room not yet furnished. Location: Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Description: Drawing-room 34 by 19 1/2 by 17 1/2 ft. looking towards Ballroom. Location: Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/771 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
